# includesMultipleApplicationVersions

**Instance Property**

A Boolean indicating if the version of the app changed at least once during the reporting period.

## Declaration

```swift
var includesMultipleApplicationVersions: Bool { get }
```

## Reading information about the payload

- **timeStampBegin**: The starting time of the reporting period.
- **timeStampEnd**: The ending time of the reporting period.
- **latestApplicationVersion**: The version of the app on the device at the end of the reporting period.
- **metaData**: A set of system-level information for the device.
